visual_description.name: outdoor_event_table_setting.jpg
visual_description.description: Tables with white cloths, peach napkins, and glassware under a tent. White chairs, simple vase flowers, balloons, gifts in background. Soft, natural light, some shadows, slightly dull colors.
visual_description.score_basis: Image has inviting feel, arranged for a celebration, but overall lighting is flat and colors lack vibrancy. Table arrangement is clear but background feels cluttered. Not professionally lit, looks casual and slightly underexposed. No fake elements apparent.
